headline: Down 11%, Is Carnival Stock a Buy?
summary: Carnival's business has long rebounded from the COVID-19 crisis, but the mountain of debt remains.  With shares down 11% since the start of the year, Carnival Corporation (NYSE: CCL) stock is probably on the radar of deal-hungry investors.  How significant is the tariff risk for Carnival?
